wikipedia_page.main: Alexander Mungo Comine Russell (born 24 May 1998), known as Mungo Russell, is an English cricketer.He made his first-class debut on 1 April 2018 for Durham MCCU against Warwickshire as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. In June 2020 he received a half palatinate from Team Durham for his cricketing activities as a student.
